      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values compared against bench-top hemolysis measurements at all 5 operating points. Mean absolute percentage error is 18.4%. All predictions fall within the 25% acceptance band. Worst-case operating point correctly identified by CFD at 6 L/min, 4000 RPM."
    },
    {
