    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model correctly identifies the worst-case hemolysis operating point and predicts NIH within 18.4% of bench measurements across all 5 operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable under MRL 2 scoping guidance. The UnitOfAssurance is accepted for regulatory submission supporting Class II 510(k) clearance of the CPB device.",
